description: Cadbury Cookies Choc Centre is not your ordinary chocolate chip cookie with its wonderful crunch and rich chocolate filling. It contains crunchy cookies with choc filled centre. Eat me Warm and heat me up in the microwave. Pop me in the microwave oven for 10 seconds for a delicious warm treat.
